<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV115">
<l>attaṉāki yaṉṉaiyāki yāḷumempi rāṉumā</l>
<l>yottovvāta palpiṟappo ḻittunammai yāṭkoḷvāṉ</l>
<l>muttaṉārmu kuntaṉārpu kuntunammuḷ mēviṉār,</l>
<l>ettiṉāli ṭarkkaṭaṟki ṭattiyēḻai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being the father, the mother, and our Lord who rules, the [Lord of] liberation,</l>
<l>Mukunda entered and lived among us in order to accept us as [His] servants,</l>
<l>destroying [our] many similar and dissimilar births.</l>
<l>Why do you lie in the ocean of distress, o wretched heart!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
